1
00:00:06,349 --> 00:00:10,707
All suffering is due
to separation from Kṛṣṇa.

2
00:00:10,707 --> 00:00:14,061
In the lower stages
of conditional existence,

3
00:00:14,061 --> 00:00:17,866
and the higher stages
of unconditional existence,

4
00:00:17,866 --> 00:00:21,456
the cure is one.

5
00:00:21,456 --> 00:00:24,329
Talk about Kṛṣṇa, hear about Kṛṣṇa.

6
00:00:24,329 --> 00:00:29,505
Śrotavyaḥ kīrtitavyaś cha
smartavyaś chechchhatābhayam (SB: 2.1.5)

7
00:00:29,505 --> 00:00:33,611
Hear about Kṛṣṇa,

8
00:00:33,611 --> 00:00:36,703
chant about Kṛṣṇa, remember Kṛṣṇa.

